product.name: WIRED Effect: Bot changes clothes
product.description: This effect changes the clothes of the selected Bot

product.name: WIRED Effect: Bot follows user
product.description: This effect makes the selected Bot follow the triggering users

product.name: WIRED Effect: Bot gives Handitem
product.description: This effect makes the selected Bot give the selected handitem

product.name: WIRED Effect: Bot moves to Furni
product.description: This effect makes the selected Bot move to one of the selected Furni

product.name: WIRED Effect: Bot talks or whispers to all users
product.description: This effect makes the selected Bot talk or shout to all users

product.name: WIRED Effect: Bot talks or whispers to user
product.description: This effect makes the selected Bot talk or whisper to the triggering user

product.name: WIRED Effect: Teleport Bot to Furni
product.description: This effect teleports the selected Bot to one of the selected Furni

product.name: WIRED EFFECT: Execute Wired Stacks
product.description: This Wired allows you to select 5 wired stacks to execute from a single trigger, regardless of existing conditions or triggers.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Move Furni towards nearest user
product.description: This Effect moves the Furnis towards nearest user in the same row or column. If there is a user next to this furni, WIRED Trigger: User stuff collision will activate.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Move Furni away from nearest user
product.description: This Effect moves the selected Furnis away from the nearest user in the same row or column. If there is user next to this Furni, WIRED Trigger: User stuff collision will activate.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Give Points
product.description: This Effect gives the set amount of points to the team that triggers the Effect. You can also choose how many times in a game the amount can be given.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Give score to a predefined team
product.description: This Effect gives the set amount of points to a team of your choosing. You can also choose how many times in a game the score can be given.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Join team
product.description: This Effect makes the triggering user join a team of your choosing.

product.name: WIRED EFFECT: Kick User
product.description: This effect kicks a user depending on the triggering criteria

product.name: WIRED Effect: Leave Team
product.description: This Effect makes the triggering user leave their current team.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Match Furni to Position & State
product.description: This Effect returns the selected Furni to its set conditions.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Move Triggering Furni
product.description: This Effect moves a Furni defined by the Trigger to the vicinity of one of the selected Furnis.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Move And Rotate Furni
product.description: This effect moves and rotates the selected Furni

product.name: WIRED Effect: Change Furni Direction
product.description: This Effect changes the Furnis direction. When the move is blocked, Furni will change direction based on setting. If there is a user next to the Furni, WIRED Trigger: User stuff collision will activate.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Mute user
product.description: This Effect mutes the triggering user.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Toggle furni state
product.description: This Effect changes the state of the chosen furni as though the furni has just been double clicked.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Timer Reset
product.description: This Effect resets triggers that use timers.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Show Message
product.description: This effect shows a secret message only to the triggering users.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Teleport To Furni
product.description: This Effect teleports the triggering user to a Furni. If you select more than one Furni, the user is randomly teleported to one of them.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Toggle Furni State
product.description: This Effect changes the state of the chosen Furni as if the Furni has just been double clicked.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Toggle Furni to Random State
product.description: This Effect changes the state of the chosen furni randomly.

product.name: WIRED GAME: Super Blob
product.description: Used in WIRED games. User/ team receives five points when collected. Can be controlled by WIRED Furni.

product.name: Blob
product.description: Awards 5 points to the collecting team

product.name: Blob
product.description: Awards 1 point to the collecting team - can be made visible with switch state wired (you'll need to use the :furni command)

product.name: WIRED GAME: Blob
product.description: Used in WIRED games. User/ team receives a point when collected.

product.name: Puzzle Box
product.description: Stand beside the box and double click to push it away from you.

product.name: WIRED CONDITION: Group Member
product.description: Condition passes when this is a group room and the avatar is a member of that group

product.name: WIRED Condition: User Is In Team x
product.description: Triggering is allowed if the triggerering user belongs to the selected team.

product.name: Viking Wired
product.description: Allows you to set a specific date/time range for the wired effect to work.

product.name: WIRED Condition: Furnis have avatars
product.description: Triggering is allowed if all the picked furnis have avatars on them.

product.name: WIRED Condition: Has Furni On
product.description: Triggering is allowed if one of the chosen Furni has another Furni on it. The Furni on top can then be acted upon with Effects.

product.name: WIRED Condition: User has handitem
product.description: Triggering is allowed if the user is holding the selected handitem

product.name: WIRED Condition: Furni States And Positions Match
product.description: Triggering is allowed if the states and positions of the selected Furni match.

product.name: WIRED Negative Condition: Has NO Furni On
product.description: Triggering is allowed if one of the chosen Furni has NO other Furni on it.

product.name: WIRED Negative Condition: Furnis have NO avatars
